=== Reconstruction View ===

image:screenshot3.png[]

`------------------------`----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Application  		    Description-
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Globe View (4)	   	   The region of the main window which displays a graphical representation of the globe and the features on it. 
Time Controls (7)	   A collection of user-interface controls for precise control of the reconstruction time.
Zoom Controls (8)	   A collection of user-interface controls for precise control of the Globe View camera zoom.
Zoom Slider (9)		   A mouse-controlled slider which controls the zoom level of the Globe View camera.
Camera Coordinate (10)	   An information field which indicates the current globe position of the Globe View camera
Mouse Coordinate (11) 	   An information field which indicates the current globe position of the mouse pointer.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

